txt.en: The Roving Threats of Southern Mirkwood
In your absence, new threats have come to Southern Mirkwood. Gellamiel, an Elf in Ost Galadh, seeks the assistance of a brave hero as she works to fend off the forces of Dol Guldur.
Gellamiel can be found in Ost Galadh.\n\nYou should speak with Gellamiel.
'We Elves continue to battle the forces of Dol Guldur. They have begun a renewed effort to push back our forces these past few days and we could use any able warriors to defend these woods.'
Gellamiel can be found in Ost Galadh.\n\nYou should speak with Gellamiel.
Gellamiel requires assistance as Southern Mirkwood is once again under threat.
